## Recommended Printer Settings

These settings apply to all parts unless a part-specific note overrides them.

| Setting                | Value                                              |
|------------------------|----------------------------------------------------|
| **Layer height**       | 0.2 mm (use 0.12 mm for face panels — parts 4 & 8) |
| **Infill**             | 20% Gyroid                                         |
| **Walls / perimeters** | 3                                                  |
| **Top/bottom layers**  | 5                                                  |
| **Print speed**        | 50 mm/s (40 mm/s for detail parts)                 |
| **Nozzle temp**        | 210 °C (PLA) / 230 °C (PETG)                       |
| **Bed temp**           | 60 °C (PLA) / 70 °C (PETG)                         |
| **Cooling**            | 100% part cooling fan                              |
| **Supports**           | See per-part notes below                           |

### Recommended Filament

- **Primary body parts (1, 2, 3, 7):** White or light grey PLA/PETG — easy to paint or leave as-is
- **Face & display panels (4, 8):** Black PLA — creates visual contrast for display cutouts
- **Clips (5, 6):** PETG preferred for flexibility and grip

