## Per-Part Print Instructions

### Part 1 — Head / Side Housing
`obj_1_Yeti Full.stl_1.stl` | 40 × 31 × 38 mm

- **Orientation:** Place the largest flat face on the bed
- **Supports:** Yes — enable for any overhangs > 45°
- **Infill:** 20%
- **Notes:** This is a structural housing; go 3 walls minimum. Check fit with Part 7 before final print.

