## Troubleshooting

| Issue                     | Cause                           | Fix                                        |
|---------------------------|---------------------------------|--------------------------------------------|
| Panel (part 4/8) warping  | Thin flat part cooling unevenly | Add brim 3 mm, slow first layer to 20 mm/s |
| Layer separation on clips | PETG under-extruded             | Raise temp +5 °C, check E-steps            |
| Rough surface on body (7) | Layer lines too coarse          | Drop to 0.16 mm layer height               |
| Supports hard to remove   | Too many contact points         | Switch to tree supports, 0.2 mm Z gap      |
| Fit too tight between parts | Elephant foot on first layer  | Enable first-layer compensation (−0.1 mm)  |

